(229, 7, 'essay', 'Here are three different types of processing methods. For each processing method, provide an appropriate application.\n- Batch Processing: ‚Ä¶\n- Real-Time Processing: ‚Ä¶\n- Transaction Processing: ‚Ä¶', 3, '- Batch processing: Payroll system.\n- Real-time processing: Flight reservation system.\n- Transaction processing: Point of sale system.', 'Different processing types are used in distinct applications such as payroll, reservations, and sales.', NULL, NULL, NULL),
