(231, 7, 'essay', 'Kazizela Manufactures is planning to computerize their manual order processing system. A system analyst is hired, but the proposed change does not meet the requirements in the feasibility study. What should the analyst do in this case?', 1, '- The analyst would recommend revisiting the feasibility study to identify where the requirements were misunderstood or incorrect.', 'If the system proposal does not meet feasibility, the project may need re-scoping or adjustments.', NULL, NULL, NULL),
